(27,1,"2019-05-21 21:22:38","2019-05-21 21:22:38","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Flutter is Google’s portable UI toolkit for building beautiful, natively-compiled applications for mobile, web, and desktop from a single codebase. Paint your app to life in milliseconds with stateful Hot Reload. Use a rich set of fully-customizable widgets to build native interfaces in minutes. Quickly ship features with a focus on native end-user experiences. Layered architecture allows for full customization, which results in incredibly fast rendering and expressive and flexible designs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","What the Flutter","","publish","open","open","","what-the-flutter","","","2019-05-21 21:34:51","2019-05-21 21:34:51","",0,"http://jsbaidwan.local/?p=27",0,"post","",0),
